==Enemies==
{{Main|Soul Blazer:Enemies}}

Soul Blazer features over 50 enemy types across 6 acts, spawning from Soul Lairs.

==Items and Equipment==
{{Main|Soul Blazer:Items}}

Equipment includes 8 swords, 8 armor pieces, and 8 magic types.

==Audio==
The game's music was composed by Yukihide Takekawa. The SNES SPC700 audio driver is located at $07A7F6 in the ROM.

===Soundtrack===
The game features 26 unique music tracks:
* Title Screen, The Shrine, area themes for each act
* Boss Battle, Deathtoll (final boss)
* Victory, Game Over, Ending, Credits

